user.description: Hey there, sorry I killed you! I truly hope that you can rebound from this, and go on to get a higher score after respawning. If you're getting off the game after reading this, then I hope you have a great rest of your day!
user.about: I don't use hacks or HaliButt for my high scores. I like to main Walrus, Sunfish or Marlin, and enjoy Bowhead and Beaked Whale in PD.
